  "prompt": "What are the best available social media analytics tool?",
  "response": "As of the latest information, here are some of the top social media analytics tools that are widely regarded for their effectiveness and comprehensive features:\n\n1. **Hootsuite**: Known for its scheduling capabilities, Hootsuite also offers robust analytics features to track performance across multiple social media platforms, providing insights into engagement, reach, and more.\n\n2. **Sprout Social**: This tool excels in offering detailed analytics, reporting, and social listening capabilities. It helps in understanding audience interactions and tracking key metrics.\n\n3. **Buffer**: Beyond scheduling posts, Buffer provides in-depth analytics to monitor performance, including reach and engagement metrics. The tool is user-friendly and provides clear reports.\n\n4. **Mention**: Focused heavily on social listening, Mention helps track brand mentions and sentiment analysis across social media and the web. It\u2019s great for monitoring brand reputation and competitor activity.\n\n5. **Brandwatch**: This tool is highly regarded for its advanced social listening and analytics capabilities. It helps analyze consumer insights and trends across social media.\n\n6. **Socialbakers**: Known for its AI-powered analytics, Socialbakers offers comprehensive performance metrics of both paid and organic content, audience analysis, and competitive benchmarking.\n\n7. **Google Analytics (Social Media Reports)**: While primarily a web analytics tool, Google Analytics also offers detailed social media reports that allow you to track the performance of social campaigns and traffic driven from social media.\n\n8. **BuzzSumo**: BuzzSumo is excellent for content research and performance analytics. It helps track the virality of posts, influencer engagement, and trending topics.\n\n9. **SEMrush**: Although it's widely known as an SEO tool, SEMrush also provides valuable social media analytics features like tracking brand mentions, analyzing competitors, and measuring campaign performance.\n\n10. **Keyhole**: Keyhole offers real-time tracking for social media campaigns and hashtags, providing insightful analytics on engagement and reach.\n\nThese tools provide various features tailored to different aspects of social media management and analytics, from performance tracking and audience engagement to social listening and competitive analysis. The best tool for you will depend on your specific needs, budget, and the platforms you are focusing on.",
